summary:
I hope Taylor knows someday that she is what gets me through my best and worst days. 
She was my comfort when I had no friends...
body:
I hope Taylor knows someday that she is what gets me through my best and worst days.

She was my comfort when I had no friends to sit with at lunch.

She is my go-to person when people are nothing but mean

She’s my partner on the way to work.

The person who dragged me through body dysmorphia.

My relaxation during my early morning coffee.

My duo partner when I’m in the shower.

The friend rubbing my back as I cry over heartbreak, trying to get clean

The friend telling me over and over that I CAN do this, I can get past this, I can overcome this, that things change

And the friend telling me I’m worth the world.

Taylor, you are my best friend. Thank you for 13 wonderful years thus far, and thank you for the many more years to come.

summary: I’m so glad that Taylor isn’t dieting as much anymore and has allowed herself to gain weight because she finally looks healthy....
body:
I’m so glad that Taylor isn’t dieting as much anymore and has allowed herself to gain weight because she finally looks healthy. Like, seeing her at awards shows and stuff she doesn’t look ‘fat’ or whatever the media tried to tell her: she just looks healthy. Which I’m so so SO glad about bc I see edits and pictures and videos of her in 1989 era and I’m so scared for her. My first reaction is always “oh my god was she eating? I hope she was eating” and I’m so glad we don’t have to be concerned anymore because she’s looking so happy and gorgeous

@taylorswift I’m so glad you’re doing better than you ever have!
